e trader. In addition, the company offers modular kitchens, wardrobes, accessories, system aluminum windows and doors, kitchen sinks, faucets, and veneers; ACP and cladding, paints, and flooring solutions; and electrical wires and cables, electrical fittings and switches, and fans and exhaust fans. The company operates under the Taurus, Vaigai Sanitation, Fotia Ceramica, Ganga, and Vishal Precision Tubes brand name. It serves homeowners, architect, contractors, interior designers, developers, plumbers, and electricians. The company was formerly known as Shankara Infrastructure Materials Limited and changed its name to Shankara Building Products Limited in July 2006. Shankara Building Products Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Bengaluru, India."}}